SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students a, Enrollments b WHERE a.Department = 'ECE' AND ( (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%') OR (a.Department = 'ECE' AND a.NetId = b.NetId AND b.CRN IN (SELECT CRN FROM Courses WHERE Department = 'CS')) ) ORDER BY a.NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students s WHERE (a.Department ='ECE' ) AND (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%'   OR a.NetId IN (SELECT e.NetId FROM Enrollments e JOIN Courses c ON e.CRN = c.CRN  WHERE c.Department='CS')) ORDER BY NetId DESC;

SELECT FirstName, LastName, NetId FROM Courses a NATURAL JOIN Enrollments b NATURAL JOIN (SELECT FirstName, LastName, NetId                                             FROM Students                                             WHERE Department = 'ECE') as ECEstud WHERE a.Department = 'CS' or FirstName LIKE 'T%' GROUP BY NetId ORDER BY NetId DESC

SELECT b.FirstName, b.LastName, b.NetID FROM Enrollments as a  INNER JOIN Students as b on b.NetId = a.NetId WHERE b.Department = 'ECE' AND (b.FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR a.CRN IN  (SELECT a.CRN  FROM Enrollments as a  INNER JOIN Courses as C on C.CRN = a.CRN WHERE C.Department = 'CS')) GROUP BY b.NetId ORDER BY b.NetId DESC

Select DISTINCT FirstName, LastName, NetId From Students Where Department = "ECE" AND FirstName LIKE "T%" OR Department = "ECE" AND NetID in (                                                               Select DISTINCT NetID                                                               From Enrollments e Natural Join Courses c                                                               Where c.Department = "CS"                                                                                 ) Order By NetID DESC;

select FirstName,LastName,NetId from Students where Department = 'ECE' and NetId in  (select DISTINCT NetId from Enrollments as E inner join Courses as C on E.CRN = C.CRN where C.Department = 'CS') order by NetId DESC;

Select Distinct FirstName, LastName, Students.NetId From Students,     (SELECT NetId      From   Enrollments, (SELECT CRN                           FROM Courses                           Where Department LIKE 'CS') as temp1      WHERE Enrollments.CRN LIKE temp1.CRN      ) as temp2 Where Students.NetID like temp2.NetID AND Students.Department like 'ECE' GROUP BY Students.NetId Desc;

SELECT FirstName, LastName, NetId FROM Students S WHERE Department = 'ECE' AND ((FirstName LIKE 'T%') OR EXISTS (     SELECT CRN     FROM Enrollments NATURAL JOIN Courses     WHERE NetId = a.NetId AND Department = 'CS'     ) ) ORDER BY NetId desc;

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students s WHERE a.Department = 'ECE' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Enrollments e, Courses c WHERE a.NetId = e.NetId AND e.CRN = c.CRN AND c.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY NetId DESC

SELECT FirstName, LastName, NetId FROM (SELECT * FROM Students WHERE Department = 'ECE') as EStudents WHERE FirstName like 'T%' OR NetId in(     SELECT DISTINCT NetId from Enrollments where CRN in(         SELECT CRN from Courses WHERE Department = 'CS'         ) ) Order BY NetId DESC

select distinct FirstName, LastName, NetId  from Students where Department="ECE" and (FirstName="T%" or NetID in (select NetID from Enrollments where CRN in (select CRN from Courses where Department="CS"))) Order by NetId desc

SELECT DISTINCT FirstName, LastName, Students.NetId FROM Students WHERE Department = 'ECE' AND (FirstName = 'T%' OR Students.NetId IN (     SELECT Enrollments.NetId     FROM Enrollments LEFT JOIN Courses     ON Enrollments.CRN = Courses.CRN     WHERE Courses.Department = 'CS' )) ORDER BY Students.NetId DESC

SELECT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetID FROM Students a, (Select C.NetId                  From Enrollments C Natural Join Courses D                 Where D.Department = 'CS'                 Group By C.NetId                 Having COUNT(D.Department) > 0) as b Where (a.Department = 'ECE' AND a.FirstName LIKE 'T%') or (a.Department = 'ECE' AND a.NetId = b.NetId) GROUP BY a.NETID ORDER BY a.NetId DESC

Department	                               FROM Courses                               WHERE Courses.Department='CS')) GROUP BY NetID  #SELECT FirstName, LastName, NetID, Department #FROM Students NATURAL JOIN Courses a Department = ANY  (SELECT Department  #           FROM Courses #            WHERE Department= 'CS') #GROUP BY NetID

select distinct S.FirstName, S.LastName, S.NetId from ((Enrollments E inner join Students S                                     on E.NetId = S.NetId) inner join Courses C                                     on E.CRN = C.CRN) where S.Department = 'ECE' and (S.FirstName like 'T%' or C.Department = 'CS') order by S.NetId desc;

select a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId from Students S where a.Department = "ECE" and (a.FirstName = "T%" or exists (select 1                                   from Enrollments E Natural Join Courses C                                   where E.NetId = a.NetId and C.Department = "CS")) order by a.Netid DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT Students.FirstName, Students.LastName, Students.NetId FROM Students, Enrollments, Courses WHERE (Students.NetId = Enrollments.NetId AND Students.Department = 'ECE' AND Students.FirstName LIKE 'T%') OR (Students.NetId = Enrollments.NetId AND Students.Department = 'ECE' AND Enrollments.CRN = Courses.CRN AND Courses.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY Students.NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT * FROM  (SELECT * FROM      (     SELECT FirstName, LastName, NetId     FROM Students     WHERE FirstName LIKE 'T%' AND Department = 'ECE'     ) AS T1 UNION SELECT * FROM     (     SELECT FirstName, LastName, NetId     FROM Students      WHERE Department = "ECE" AND     NetId IN          (         SELECT NetId         FROM Enrollments E         NATURAL JOIN Courses C         WHERE C.Department = "CS"         )     ) AS T2 ) AS T3 ORDER BY NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT FirstName, LastName, NetId FROM Students WHERE Department = 'ECE' AND  		(FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR          NetId IN (SELECT DISTINCT NetId 			FROM Enrollments JOIN Courses 				ON Enrollments.CRN = Courses.CRN             WHERE Department = 'CS')) ORDER BY NetId DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT Students.FirstName, Students.LastName, Students.NetId FROM Students  INNER JOIN Enrollments ON Students.NetId = Enrollments.NetId  INNER JOIN Courses ON Enrollments.CRN = Courses.CRN WHERE Students.Department = 'ECE' AND ((Students.FirstName LIKE 'T%') OR Courses.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY Students.NetId DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students a, Enrollments b, Courses c WHERE ((a.Department = 'ECE') AND (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%')) OR (a.Department = 'ECE' AND a.NetId IN (SELECT e2.NetId FROM Enrollments e2, Courses c2                 WHERE e2.CRN = c2.CRN AND c2.Department ='CS')) ORDER BY a.NetId desc

SELECT FirstName, LastName, NetId  FROM Students  WHERE Department = 'ECE' AND (FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR NetID IN (SELECT e.NetId FROM Enrollments e NATURAL JOIN Courses c WHERE c.Department = 'CS')) ORDER BY NetId DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT     a.FirstName,     a.LastName,     a.NetId FROM     Students a      JOIN Enrollments E         ON a.NetId = b.NetId     JOIN Courses C         ON b.CRN = c.CRN WHERE     a.Department = "ECE"     AND (         a.FirstName LIKE "T%"         OR         c.Department = "CS"     ) ORDER BY     a.NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT Students.FirstName, Students.LastName, Students.NetId FROM Students JOIN Enrollments ON Students.NetId = Enrollments.NetId JOIN Courses ON Courses.CRN = Enrollments.CRN WHERE (Students.Department = 'ECE' AND Students.FirstName LIKE "T%") OR (Students.Department = 'ECE' AND Courses.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY Students.NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetID FROM Students a, Enrollments b, Courses c WHERE a.Department = 'ECE' and (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%' or (b.NetId = a.NetID and b.CRN = c.CRN and c.Department = 'CS')) ORDER BY NetID DESC

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students S JOIN Enrollments b ON a.NetId = b.NetId JOIN Courses c ON b.CRN = c.CRN WHERE a.Department = "ECE" AND LEFT(a.FirstName, 1) = "T"  OR a.Department = "ECE" AND c.Department = "CS" ORDER BY a.NetId;

SELECT DISTINCT FirstName, LastName, a.NetId FROM Students a, Enrollments b, Courses c WHERE a.Department = 'ECE' AND (FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR (a.NetId = b.NetId AND b.CRN = c.CRN AND c.Department = 'CS')) ORDER BY a.NetId DESC

select FirstName, LastName, NetId from Students where NetId in (select distinct S.NetId from Students S, Enrollments E, Courses C where S.department = "ECE" &&      ((S.NetId = E.NetId && E.crn = C.crn && C.Department = "CS") || S.FirstName like "T%"))

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students S WHERE a.Department = 'ECE' and (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%' or EXISTS (SELECT*                                     FROM Enrollments E, Courses C                                     WHERE E.NetId = a.NetID and E.CRN = C.CRN and C.Department = 'CS'                                                                 ))   ORDER BY a.NetId DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students s WHERE a.Department LIKE "ECE" AND (a.FirstName LIKE "T%" OR EXISTS ( SELECT e.NetId FROM Enrollments e JOIN Courses c ON c.CRN = e.CRN WHERE c.Department LIKE "CS" AND e.NetId = a.NetId)) ORDER BY a.NetId DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT Firstname, Lastname, NetId FROM Students WHERE (Department='ECE' AND Firstname LIKE 'T%') OR (Department='ECE' AND NetId in(SELECT NetId FROM Enrollments natural join Courses WHERE Department='CS')) ORDER BY NetId DESC

select Students.FirstName, Students.LastName, Students.NetId from Students where Students.Department = 'ECE'  AND (Students.FirstName like 'T%' OR exists (   SELECT Enrollments.NetId, Enrollments.CRN   FROM Enrollments   inner join (     select Courses.CRN, Courses.Department     from Courses     where Courses.Department = 'CS'   ) as g on g.CRN = Enrollments.CRN   where Enrollments.NetId = Students.NetId )) order by Students.NetId desc;

Select Distinct a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students S JOIN Enrollments b ON a.NetId=b.NetId JOIN Courses c ON b.CRN=c.CRN WHERE (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%' AND a.Department = "ECE") OR (a.Department = "ECE" AND c.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY a.NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT ece.FirstName, ece.LastName, ece.NetId  FROM ((SELECT * FROM Students WHERE Department = 'ECE') AS ece NATURAL JOIN Enrollments e) JOIN Courses a ON e.CRN = a.CRN WHERE ece.NetId = ANY (SELECT DISTINCT e.NetId                                 FROM Enrollments e NATURAL JOIN Courses c                                 WHERE a.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY ece.NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId  FROM Students a, Enrollments b, Courses C  WHERE a.Department = "ECE" AND a.FirstName LIKE "T%"     OR ( a.Department = "ECE" AND a.NetId = b.NetId AND b.CRN = c.CRN          AND c.Department = "CS") ORDER BY a.NetId DESC

select distinct  a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId from Students s     left join Enrollments b on a.NetId = b.NetId     left join Courses c on b.CRN = c.CRN     where (a.Department='ECE' and c.Department='CS') or (left(a.FirstName,1)='T'and a.Department='ECE' )     order by a.NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT FirstName, LastName, a.NetId FROM Students a INNER JOIN Enrollments b ON a.NetId = b.NetId INNER JOIN Courses c ON c.CRN = b.CRN WHERE (a.Department = 'ECE' AND FirstName LIKE 'T%') OR (a.Department = 'ECE' AND c.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY NetId DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT FirstName, LastName, NetId FROM Students NATURAL JOIN Enrollments WHERE (FirstName LIKE "T%" AND Department = "ECE") or ( Department = "ECE" AND CRN IN (SELECT CRN                                           FROM Courses                                           WHERE Department = "CS"                                           )                              ) ORDER BY NetId DESC;

select distinct FirstName, LastName, NetId from Enrollments a natural join Students b join Courses c on a.CRN = c.CRN where b.Department = "ECE" and (b.FirstName like 'T%' or c.Department = "CS") order by NetId desc

SELECT DISTINCT Students.FirstName, Students.LastName, Students.NetId FROM (Students NATURAL JOIN Enrollments) JOIN Courses ON Enrollments.CRN = Courses.CRN WHERE Students.Department = 'ECE' AND (FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR Courses.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY NetId DESC;

select FirstName, LastName, NetId from Students a  where a.FirstName like "T%" and a.Department = "ECE" union select distinct FirstName, LastName, a.NetId from (Students a natural join Enrollments e) inner join Courses b on e.CRN = b.CRN  where b.Department = "CS" and a.Department = "ECE" order by NetId desc

SELECT DISTINCT S.FirstName, S.LastName, S.NetId FROM Students AS S, Enrollments AS E, Courses AS C WHERE S.Department = "ECE" AND     (S.FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR (S.NetId = E.NetId         AND E.CRN = C.CRN         AND C.Department = 'CS')) ORDER BY S.NetId DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT b.FirstName, b.LastName, b.NetId FROM Enrollments a INNER JOIN Students b ON b.NetId = a.NetId WHERE b.Department = "ECE" AND (b.FirstName LIKE "%T" OR a.CRN IN ( SELECT a.CRN FROM Enrollments a INNER JOIN Courses C on C.CRN = a.CRN WHERE C.Department = "CS" )) GROUP BY b.NetId ORDER BY b.NetId DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students a  WHERE a.Department = "ECE" AND (a.FirstName Like "T%" OR a.NetId IN  (SELECT e.NetId                 FROM Enrollments e Natural Join Courses c                 WHERE Department = "CS") ) ORDER BY a.NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students a JOIN Enrollments b JOIN Courses c ON a.NetId = b.NetId AND b.CRN = c.CRN WHERE (a.Department = 'ECE') AND (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR c.Department = 'CS') ORDER BY a.NetId DESC

select a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetID from Students a, Enrollments b, Courses c where a.Department = "ECE" and  a.NetID = b.NetID and c.CRN = b.CRN group by  a.NetID, a.FirstName, a.LastName HAVING left(a.FirstName, 1) = 'T' or sum(c.Department = "CS") >= 1 order by a.netid desc;

SELECT DISTINCT FirstName, LastName, Students.NetId  FROM Students  JOIN Enrollments ON Students.NetId = Enrollments.NetId JOIN Courses ON Courses.CRN = Enrollments.CRN WHERE  Students.Department = "ECE" AND (Courses.Department = "CS" OR FirstName LIKE 'T%') ORDER BY Students.NetId desc;

select distinct a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetID from Students a, Enrollments b, Courses c where a.Department = 'ECE' and (a.FirstName like 'T%' or (a.NetId = b.NetId and b.CRN=c.CRN and c.Department = 'CS')) order by a.NetId desc;

SELECT DISTINCT FirstName, LastName, Students.NetId FROM Students WHERE Department = 'ECE'  AND (FirstName LIKE 'T%'  OR NetId IN ( SELECT Enrollments.NetId  FROM Enrollments NATURAL JOIN Courses WHERE Courses.Department = 'CS' ) ) ORDER BY NetId DESC

select FirstName, LastName, NetId from Students where Department = 'ECE' AND      (FirstName like 'T%' OR EXISTS (select * from Enrollments natural join Courses where Department = 'CS' and NetId = Students.NetId)) order by NetId DESC;

SELECT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetID  From Students S Where a.Department = "ECE" AND (a.Firstname LIKE 'T%' OR EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM Enrollments E LEFT OUTER JOIN Courses C ON E.CRN = C.CRN Where C.Department = "CS" AND E.NetID = a.NetID)) ORDER BY NetID DESC;

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students a, Enrollments b, Courses c WHERE a.Department = 'ECE' AND (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR  (a.NetId = b.NetId AND b.CRN = c.CRN AND c.Department = 'CS')) ORDER BY NetId DESC

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, NetId FROM Students S NATURAL JOIN Enrollments E LEFT OUTER JOIN Courses c ON b.CRN = c.CRN WHERE (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%' AND a.Department LIKE 'ECE')     OR (a.Department LIKE 'ECE' AND c.Department LIKE 'CS') ORDER BY NetId DESC

SELECT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students s WHERE a.Department = 'ECE' AND (a.FirstName LIKE 'T%' OR a.NetId IN (SELECT e.NetId FROM Enrollments e NATURAL JOIN Courses c WHERE c.Department = 'CS')) order by a.NetId desc

SELECT DISTINCT a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId FROM Students S      JOIN Enrollments b ON a.NetId = b.NetId      JOIN Courses c ON b.CRN = c.CRN WHERE a.Department = 'ECE' AND (c.Department = 'CS' OR a.FirstName LIKE 'T%') ORDER BY a.NetID DESC

select distinct a.FirstName, a.LastName, a.NetId from Students a inner join Enrollments b on a.NetId = b.NetId inner join Courses c on b.CRN = c.CRN where a.Department = "ECE" and (c.Department = "CS" or a.FirstName like "T%") order by a.NetId desc

select FirstName, LastName, NetId from Students where Department = "ECE" and (     FirstName like "T%"     or NetId in (         select NetId         from Enrollments natural join (             select *             from Courses             where Department = "CS"         ) t1     ) ) order by NetId desc

SELECT Students.FirstName, Students.LastName, Students.NetId FROM Students INNER JOIN Enrollments ON Students.NetId = Enrollments.NetID INNER JOIN Courses ON Enrollments.CRN = Courses.CRN WHERE Students.Department = 'ECE' AND (Students.NetId LIKE 'T%' OR Courses.Department = 'CS') GROUP BY Students.NetId ORDER BY Students.NetId DESC;
